701990f-b.text:
(1-2)
Van Nest Avenue, at the S.E. corner of White Plains Road, showing the Roman Catholic Church of Our Lady of Solace.
P.L.Sperr  View 1: July 18, 192S
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2: July 28, 19a8
(3) The saae, sowe years later, showing the church edifice being
occupied by the Enights of Wolumbus.
P.L.Sperr  June 22, 1940
